      "text": "{user}さん\nちょっと相談いいですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nCan we talk?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.866666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 8.533333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、私心配なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m worried‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、分かるよ。まだ場慣れしてないから当然だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. It’s a natural reaction when you’re inexperienced—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 16.666666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　自分じゃなくて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? Not for yourself?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 20.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "だって今日の琴乃ちゃん\n朝からずっと難しい顔してるんですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan has looked\non edge all morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "さっきもず～っとステージの袖から会場を見てて\n私がそばにいるのにも気付かないくらい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She keeps peeking out at the audience from the stage wings.\nShe didn’t even notice that I was right beside her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "多分、お客さんの入りを気にしてるんだろうな\n琴乃は自分に厳しいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s probably concerned about the turnout.\nKotono tends to be hard on herself‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 37.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよね……デビューライブは沢山お客さんが\n来てくれたのに、前回はあんまりだったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… We had a big crowd for our debut live‚\nbut last time wasn’t so great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "……どうしたらいいんでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 47.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "私がもっと琴乃ちゃんの、月ストのために\n役立てることはあるんでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is there even anything I can do to help\nKotono-chan and Moon Tempest?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（……こんなテンションじゃ、いいパフォーマンスは）\n（出来ないぞ。そして、何よりも渚は――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She can’t give a good performance with her energy like this.)\n(Plus‚ there’s something Nagisa needs to know.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "渚は二つ誤解をしているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ there are two things you’ve misunderstood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 63.833333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "誤解……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Misunderstood?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "デビューライブはマスコミ関係者が多いんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were a lot of media folks at the debut live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、前回から彼らの空席は出来たが\nファンの数は増えているから安心してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that your previous live had empty seats‚\nbut there was an increase in the number of fans‚ so don’t worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 75.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "担当アイドルにそんな変な嘘はつかないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why would I lie about this to an idol I’m managing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 80.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、じゃあ{user}さんは\n私達に嘘をつかないんですね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… do you mean\nyou would never lie to us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 85.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃあ早速{user}さんの\n恋愛事情を教えて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then…\nTell me more about your love life‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.30384318033855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それ、仕事と関係ないだろう\nプライベートは勘弁してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That doesn’t have anything to do with work.\nCan we keep private matters‚ well‚ private?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 95.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、分かってますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Of course. I was just kidding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは\n仕事が恋人ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\nbut you married to your work‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 101.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "馬鹿にしてないか？\n実際そうかもしれないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now you’re just making fun of me.\nNot that I can really deny it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ごめんなさい\nでもお客さん増えてるって聞けてホッとしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Sorry.\nBut I’m relieved to hear there were more fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "早く琴乃ちゃんにも伝えてあげないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should let Kotono-chan know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 115.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
