      "text": "それに、渚。君もいてこその月のテンペストなんだ\n誰が欠けても、代わりなんていない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ Moon Tempest isn’t the same without Nagisa.\nYou’re an irreplaceable member.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃だけじゃない。五人とも\nファンにとって、俺にとって、特別な存在なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not just about Kotono.\nAll five of you are special to the fans and to me.",
