      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "（今日もみんな、よく頑張ってくれたな）\n（特に渚は、心なしか普段より堂々としていた気がする）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(They gave everything they had.)\n(Nagisa‚ in particular‚ seemed to perform with more confidence than usual.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、琴乃ちゃん。今日のライブ\n凄く盛り上がったね。私、楽しかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Kotono-chan‚ today’s live\nwent really well. I had a lot of fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs025.m4a",
      "text": "実は私、ライブの前、心配なことがあったんだ\n……何って？　ふふ、内緒だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was worried before the live.\n…About what? Hehe. That’s a secret.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs026.m4a",
      "text": "でもステージに立って、琴乃ちゃんと一緒に歌って\nダンスをしてたら、どこかに飛んでいっちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But once I’m on stage‚ singing and dancing with Kotono-chan‚\nall my worries just flew away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs027.m4a",
      "text": "だからありがとう、琴乃ちゃん\nこれからも月ストで一緒に頑張っていこうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Kotono-chan.\nLet’s keep working hard together in Moon Tempest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
